Technical SEO .......... 85/100  ████████▌░  (2 issues)
Accessibility .......... 62/100  ██████▏░░░  (5 issues)
Core Web Vitals ........ 71/100  ███████░░░  (3 issues)
Image SEO .............. 58/100  █████▊░░░░  (4 issues)
